g.text: Files containing codes of all nordic stock exchange listed companies.
- Fetch stock metrics per ticker from Yahoo Finance API.
- Score stocks through composite metrics of alg1
based on EBIT, Enterprise Value, and ROE from
"the little book that beats the market".
Largest gets 1 point, second largest 2, etc.
2. Rank each stock by ROC or ROE.
Largest gets 1 point, second largest 2, etc.
3. Get each stocks final score by summing over all points.
The smaller final score the better.
